These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, camping, singing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | traveling | camping | singing   |
| Birthday      | march    | december  | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Game      | snooker | poker     | whist      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | chess | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, fish, ferret
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, card-games
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Pet   | frog | ferret  | fish       |
| Hobby       | puzzles     | fishing | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, motorbike
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, tennis
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport    | motorbike    | bike     | airplane |
| Sport   | tennis | climbing | skiing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
City: liverpool, new-york, boston
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff, prince
1. the davidoff-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| City         | new-york | liverpool     | boston |
| Cigar   | prince        | game | davidoff    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, milk
City: san-francisco, colone, edinburgh
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person drinking milk is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Beverage        | milk | 7up      | soy-milk  |
| City   | san-francisco       | colone | edinburgh |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, cycling
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, argentine
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the pakistani##1
3. the japanese is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Sport   | cycling      | weightlifting     | snowboarding    |
| Nationality           | japanese | argentine | pakistani |

