.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, hedgehog
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, analyst, project-manager
1. the analyst is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Pet    | hedgehog | mouse | rabbit      |
| Job   | musician     | project-manager | analyst |

