.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, climbing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport      | rowing   | badminton    | climbing    |
| Birthday   | may | august | january |

