.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, musical, disaster
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, amber
1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | disaster   | musical  |
| Color   | amber    | grey | ivory |

