House: futuristic, townhouse, art-deco
1. the chef is in the middle##1
2. the accountant is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job   | accountant    | chef     | analyst   |
| House   | townhouse | futuristic | art-deco |

