.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, orange, lilac
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, fonseca, blend
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Color   | red    | lilac | orange |
| Cigar   | blend | swisher     | fonseca        |

