.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, scientific
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber, lime
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy  | scientific | satire  |
| Food   | cucumber | lime   | raspberry |

