.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, gardening
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, van, taxi
1. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | hiking | gardening    |
| Transport        | car    | taxi | van |

