.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, country, blues
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of blues##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Birthday    | january | february   | april        |
| Music-Genre   | country    | d&b | blues |

