.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, apricot, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, disaster
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person eating apricot is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Food         | avocado | apricot | pear |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster     | scientific  |

