.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, yellow, apricot
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, coffee
1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Color    | apricot | amber       | yellow  |
| Beverage   | coffee  | milk | almond-milk |

 